2026-06-04 13:39:40,877 | DEBUG    |   ## Root cause
2026-06-04 13:39:40,877 | DEBUG    |   
2026-06-04 13:39:40,878 | DEBUG    |   The `render.AsciiJSON` method incorrectly escapes non-BMP (Basic Multilingual Plane, i.e., Unicode code points U+10000 and above, such as emojis) characters. It attempts to escape them using a single `\uXXXX` sequence, but JSON `\u` escapes are strictly 4 hexadecimal digits. Non-BMP characters
2026-06-04 13:39:40,878 | DEBUG    |   
